text: Sándor Békési (27 August 1928 - 9 March 1994) was a Hungarian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:1994 deaths Category:Hungarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Debrecen
